Product Backlog


1. As a user, I should be able to quit the program (1hr)
2. As a user, I should be able to create directories, each of which may be
	relative to the current directory or may be a full path.(1hr)
3. As a user, I should be able to change the current directory to another (1hr)
4. As a user, I am able to print a specified file, print directory and
	contents of that directory, or print a suitable message by input path. (2hr)
5. As a user, I should be able to print out the current working directory
	(including the whole path). So I know what directory I am currently
	working on. (2hr)
6. As a user, I should be able to save the current directory, and move to the
	next desired directory. So later I can immediately retrieve the old and
	most recently saved directory. (2hr)




